description: Gasporox AB provides laser sensor package colutions. The company is headquartered in Lund, Skane. The company went IPO on 2016-10-25. The firm specializes in Gas in Scattering Media Absorption Spectroscopy (GASMAS) technology. The firm provides a non-intrusive technology for gas monitoring in food and pharma packages as well as porous materials and food. The packages and content stays intact and measurements can be repeated. The firm offers stand-alone instruments, modules for automation and measurement service. The company also offers the development of customized solutions which adapt the technology to specific packages and production processes. In addition, the Company provides measurement services.
naics: Semiconductor and Other Electronic Component Manufacturing
